			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Anhydrite is a naturally occurring mineral that is typically processed for use in various industries due to its properties. It is known for being a source of sulfate, and it is often ground into powder form for use in products like cement, plaster, and in the agricultural sector. The product flow for anhydrite details the extraction and processing methods, adherence to industry standards, quality of the final product, and its various uses in different sectors. The anhydrite supplied may be part of a production mix or available directly to consumers. Information on its availability, whether at the plant or to consumers, is also included.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">硬石膏是一种天然矿物，通常因其特性而被加工用于各种行业。硬石膏以硫酸盐来源著称，并通常被磨成粉末，用于水泥、灰泥以及农业领域中的产品。硬石膏的产品流程详述了提取和加工方法、行业标准的遵循、最终产品的质量及其在不同行业的多种用途。提供的硬石膏可能是生产混合物的一部分，或直接提供给消费者。还包括其可用性的信息，无论是在工厂还是消费者手中。</common:generalComment>
